<p begin="00:00:27.261" end="00:00:28.228" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen:  WELCOME TO THE<br/>REPORT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:00:28.262" end="00:00:28.929" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THANK YOU FOR JOINING US.</span></p>
